{{mergefrom|Lucky charm|date=December 2017}} This is a '''list of lucky symbols, signs and charms'''. [[Luck]] is symbolized by a wide array of objects, numbers, symbols, plant and animal life which vary significantly in different cultures globally. The significance of each symbol is rooted in either [[folklore]], [[mythology]], [[esotericism]], [[religion]], [[tradition]], necessity or a combination thereof.
